SUPPORT COMMUNICATION - SECURITY BULLETIN

Document ID: c02522633
Version: 1

HPSBUX02587 SSRT100215 rev.1 - HP-UX Directory Server and Red Hat Directory Server for HP-UX, Local Disclosure of Information, Privilege Escalation

NOTICE: The information in this Security Bulletin should be acted upon as soon as possible.

Release Date: 2010-09-22
Last Updated: 2010-09-22

 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Potential Security Impact: Local disclosure of information, privilege escalation

Source: Hewlett-Packard Company, HP Software Security Response Team

VULNERABILITY SUMMARY
A potential security vulnerability has been identified in HP-UX Directory Server and Red Hat Directory Server for HP-UX.

The vulnerability could be exploited locally resulting in information disclosure and privilege escalation.

References: CVE-2010-3282

SUPPORTED SOFTWARE VERSIONS*: ONLY impacted versions are listed.
HP-UX Directory Server B.08.10.02 and previous,
Red Hat Directory Server B.08.00.01 and previous running on HP-UX

BACKGROUND

CVSS 2.0 Base Metrics
===========================================================
  Reference              Base Vector             Base Score
CVE-2010-3282    (AV:L/AC:L/Au:S/C:P/I:P/A:N)       3.2
===========================================================
             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

RESOLUTION

HP has provided the following upgrades to resolve these vulnerabilities.
The upgrades are available by contacting the normal HP Services support channel.

Product Version / Directory Server Depot name / SHA-1 hash

HP-UX Directory Server B.08.10.03
 HPDirSvr_B.08.10.03_HP-UX_B.11.23_IA_PA.depot / A54AED9BB3ECFC26E1B9A1F71F7A9CF59449D548

 HPDirSvr_B.08.10.03_HP-UX_B.11.31_IA_PA.depot / D0F60463E3A5D8317002F6ACC012198E9B5910D5

Red Hat Directory Server B.08.00.02 (for HP-UX)
 RHDirSvr_B.08.00.02_HP-UX_B.11.11_32_64.depot / 76E1ACCAEA3DEAEBA6733E3AC6ECBBAB1237520B

 RHDirSvr_B.08.00.02_HP-UX_B.11.23_IA_PA.depot / F766E0BED730D1E06A6E4FF6CB154258656A317A

 RHDirSvr_B.08.00.02_HP-UX_B.11.31_IA_PA.depot / D3EEAF43A3505E1388D926C49EB87A305B3C636F

MANUAL ACTIONS: Yes - Update

Install HP-UX Directory Server B.08.10.03 or subsequent
Install Red Hat Directory Server B.08.00.02 or subsequent for HP-UX

PRODUCT SPECIFIC INFORMATION

HP-UX Software Assistant: HP-UX Software Assistant is an enhanced application that replaces HP-UX Security Patch Check. It analyzes all Security Bulletins issued by HP and lists recommended actions that may apply to a specific HP-UX system. It can also download patches and create a depot automatically. For more information see: https://www.hp.com/go/swa

The following text is for use by the HP-UX Software Assistant.

